A seventy year old woman is fighting for her life at St Camillus hospital in Sori town, Migori county after a mob of about 200 people attacked her on suspicion of being a Witch. 17 houses in Mwikongo village, Kisaku sub location in Suba south sub county were also set on fire in the incident. The irate residents hit Mambi Oindi on the head with blunt objects causing injuries before cutting her left leg and hand with a machete